                  <placeName ref="loc000198">Buchs</placeName>); <bibl><ref>EKGA Salez 32.01.51,
                     Bauwirtschaft, 26.07.1783</ref></bibl> (Pfründstall in <placeName
                  ref="loc000691">Salez</placeName>) oder <bibl><ref
                     target="https://archivverzeichnis.gl.ch/home/#/content/a51cc813f952450cbf942860b376958c"
                     >LAGL AG III.2402:084</ref></bibl> (<term ref="key000216">Pfründhaus</term> in
                  <placeName ref="loc000335">Grabs</placeName>).</p>
